metadata.name: Maia 01 #1/25
metadata.description:
In the year 2301, Maia 01 is aboard the Galactic Voyager spacecraft, traveling to sector 010001 of the EGS-zs8-1 Galaxy. As a synthetic replica with the task of finding habitable planets for humanity's future, Maia 01 is determined to succeed. However, she faces a significant obstacle in the form of her co-workers, who are more interested in playing than working. Frustrated and unable to complete her own construction alone, Maia 01 must find a way to inspire her co-workers to pay attention and help her achieve their common mission. Will Maia 01 and her team overcome the challenges and find a new home for humanity, or will their mission fail?
